---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms and Agreement - FiNAN">
  <PageHeader
    title="Terms and Agreement"
    description="Effective date: April 29, 2019"
    className="bg-blue-900"
  />

  <section class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
          In accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) of
          the European Union
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
          For Filipino Nurses in the Nordic Region
        </p>

        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
          In line with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) of the
          European Union, we uphold clear and fair processing of your personal
          information. Your data will be collected, recorded, and stored for the
          purposes stated below, in compliance with EU law and any applicable
          local data protection regulations.
        </p>

        <h2
          class="mt-12 mb-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-4xl"
        >
          Details
        </h2>

        <h3
          class="mt-8 mb-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-3xl"
        >
          SCOPE OF DETAILS
        </h3>

        <h4 class="mt-6 mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
          Purpose of Processing
        </h4>

        <p class="mb-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          The information you provide will be used solely for the following:
        </p>

        <ul class="mb-6 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <li>Legitimate community purposes</li>
          <li>Emergency use, such as in the event of sudden death</li>
          <li>
            Research and statistical purposes that help understand the situation
            of Filipino nurses in the region
          </li>
          <li>
            Participation in advocacies and having a collective voice before
            policymakers
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="mt-6 mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Scope of Data</h4>

        <p class="mb-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          The data that may be collected can include:
        </p>

        <ul class="mb-6 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <li>Name</li>
          <li>Gender</li>
          <li>Country of residence</li>
          <li>Professional details (e.g., license, experience)</li>
          <li>Contact details (phone, email)</li>
          <li>Other relevant information in line with the stated purpose</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="mt-6 mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
          Individual Rights
        </h4>

        <p class="mb-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          In accordance with GDPR, you have the following rights:
        </p>

        <ul class="mb-6 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <li>The right to know how your data is used</li>
          <li>The right to request a copy of your data</li>
          <li>The right to correct or delete your data</li>
          <li>The right to withdraw consent at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="mt-6 mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
          Maintaining Confidentiality
        </h4>

        <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
          All data will be treated as confidential and will not be shared with
          unauthorized parties. Information will be kept only for a reasonable
          period for research and advocacy purposes, unless retention is
          required by law.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
          By continuing and providing your data, you acknowledge that you have
          read, understood, and agree to these terms of information use, in
          accordance with GDPR and other applicable laws.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 italic">
          <strong>Note:</strong> If you wish to withdraw your consent or have additional
          questions regarding data use, you may contact info@finan.eu.com
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
